  "texts": [
    "On all 13 variables in the Stanford MOUD Dataset, we ran the CLEAR pipeline with and without the initial NER step.",
    "When running CLEAR without NER, the only entities selected are those identified during entity augmentation (described below) with ontologies and LLMs.",
    "The selected entities were then used to retrieve sections of the note that were passed to GPT-4 to extract information about a variable of interest.",
    "We report the average F1 of the information extraction task.",
    "Once the unique clinical entities from all notes are identified, the entities relevant to the input target entity are selected."
  ],
